MySQL Shell

MySQL query and administration shell client and framework.


DEPENDENCIES
============

- cmake 
- boost (recommended 1.56)
- python 2.6+ (with python in the PATH)
- libmysqlclient 5.6+
- Nghshell-deps, which includes:
a) v8 (3.28.73)
b) gmock (recommended 1.7.0) (for unit-tests)
c) gtest 1.7.0
d) gyp




BUILD
=====

Windows instructions sample:


cd <ngshell-deps>\v8
(For Linux, see <ngshell-deps>\v8\build_linux32.sh or <ngshell-deps>\v8\build_linux64.sh)
python build\gyp_8 -Dtarget_arch=ia32 -Dcomponent=static_library
cd build
msbuild all.sln /p:Configuration=Release

cd <ngshell-deps>\ngshell-deps\v8\testing\gtest
mkdir bld
cd bld
cmake ..
msbuild gtest.sln /p:Configuration=Release

cd <ngshell>
mkdir bld
cd bld

(assuming nshell-deps is downloaded in C:\src\mysql-server\ngshell-deps)
cmake -DV8_INCLUDE_DIR=C:\src\mysql-server\ngshell-deps\v8\include -DV8_LIB_DIR=C:\src\mysql-server\ngshell-deps\v8\build\Debug\lib -DWITH_BOOST=C:\src\mysql-server\boost\boost_1_56_0 -DWITH_TESTS=1 -DWITH_GTEST=C:\src\mysql-server\ngshell-deps\v8\testing\gtest\bld ..
msbuild all.sln /p:Configuration=Release


